27:50.716 --> 27:56.003
their own way and we were on our way out to the open 
water. Did you have any trouble in the open water?

27:58.847 --> 28:01.230
Any patrol boats? After you get out of the port, it 
would be international water. So the patrol, the

28:07.598 --> 28:11.263
communist patrol boat, they don't go out that far. 
